@11153 = ~Covered in intricate designs sewn into its leather with golden thread, at first glance this girdle seems more decorative than practical. Closer examination is rewarded by the realization that it functions as far more than it appears, bestowing magical protection from hammers, clubs, and other blunt weapons to its wearer.

