Weight: 1~
@11169 = ~Chain Mail~
@11170 = ~Mail of the Hallowed Hero +3~
@11171 = ~A chain mail tunic fashioned from some sort of bright metal. It is always worn over a layer of padded fabric or soft leather to prevent chafing and lessen the impact of blows.

