Weight: 8~
@11176 = ~Engraved wings stretch across the face of this ornate shield. The silver shield, inlaid with pure sapphire, gleams with a high polish no matter how much damage it suffers or what rough environs it is carried through. Often crafted for paladins and members of holy militaristic orders, a solar aegis provides substantial protection for the pure of heart.

